                     </font>
                  </Label>
                  <Text layoutX="55.0" layoutY="509.0" strokeType="OUTSIDE" strokeWidth="0.0" text="Animation software provides the digital workspace where artists draw, move, and refine their creations. Programs like Adobe Animate, Toon Boom Harmony, Pencil2D, and Blender are widely used in both education and professional studios. In the Philippines, many animation BPO companies train artists in these platforms because of their global relevance. For example, Blender (which is free and open-source) is increasingly popular among independent Filipino animators for its 3D capabilities, while Adobe Animate remains a strong choice for 2D character animation." textAlignment="JUSTIFY" wrappingWidth="727.7760620117188">
